pai version 0.01
================

DESCRIPTION

This program is designed to control your computer's alsa audio driver. It
can be used to mute, toggle functionality, or change volume on speakers, 
headphones, or the master channel.

The control available in this program should be equal to that available
though alsamixer. Although right now, some functionality has not been
implemented yet.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This program requires these CPAN modules:

    Regexp::Grammars
    Getopt::Euclid
    Data::Dumper
    List::Util
    File::Temp
    Readonly

It also requires the executable binary:

    alsactl

